# Auto-regenerated render artifacts — produced by `puml --format png` on every
# build and by the pages.yml CI step. Source of truth is the .puml file +
# committed .svg. Do NOT track the PNG renders to avoid binary churn.
# Exceptions kept tracked:
#   - tests/visual_baselines/**/*.png  (visual regression baselines)
#   - docs/diagrams/*.png              (intentionally embedded in README/site)
docs/examples/**/*.png
